[14/01/2019 20:54:48] <font color="#ffffff">César Sarachu</font>
[14/01/2019 20:54:50] <font color="#ffffff">para "INTENSAMENTE AZULES"?</font>
[14/01/2019 20:54:55] <font color="#ffffff">-Es un actor prodigioso.</font>
